CMC Markets’s Asif Adatia Left Last Month, Telegraph Reports

-- B y   T h o m a s   B i e s h e u v e l
-- 
2011-04-24T10:44:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-24/cmc-markets-s-asif-adatia-left-last-month-telegraph-reports.html
CMC Markets Plc ’s Chief Information
Officer Asif Adatia left the company last month, the Sunday
Telegraph reported, without saying where it got the information.  Plans for a market flotation are thought to be on hold, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
